"title": "8261: generosity, God's",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8261",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The generosity of God is evident in the way in which he deals with his creation, and supremely with sinners.  God bestows his gracious gifts upon sinners in salvation, in sanctification and through the coming of the Holy Spirit.</p>\n<h2>God's generous heart</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:7-Eph1:9\">EPH 1:7–1:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod34:6-Exod34:7\">EXO 34:6–34:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps33:18-Ps33:22\">PSA 33:18–33:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:11\">MAT 7:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke15:22-Luke15:24\">LUK 15:22–15:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom11:35-Rom11:36\">ROM 11:35–11:36</a></p>\n<h2>God's generosity evident in creation</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps65:9-Ps65:13\">PSA 65:9–65:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps33:5\">PSA 33:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps68:9\">PSA 68:9</a></p>\n<h2>God's generosity evident in providence</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts14:17\">ACT 14:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen24:35\">GEN 24:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num14:8\">NUM 14:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:11\">DEU 28:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut33:23\">DEU 33:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps66:12\">PSA 66:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps78:15\">PSA 78:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps132:15\">PSA 132:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps145:7\">PSA 145:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps147:6\">PSA 147:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer31:12-Jer31:14\">JER 31:12–31:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer33:6-Jer33:9\">JER 33:6–33:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal3:10\">MAL 3:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:17\">1TI 6:17</a></p>\n<h2>God's generosity experienced in salvation</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:3\">EPH 1:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:16\">JHN 1:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:5\">ROM 5:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom10:12\">ROM 10:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:7\">EPH 2:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph3:8\">EPH 3:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:10\">COL 2:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:1\">1JN 3:1</a></p>\n<h3>His love and mercifulness towards sinners</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps116:5\">PSA 116:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps130:7\">PSA 130:7</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa55:7\">ISA 55:7</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos14:4\">HOS 14:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:7\">EPH 2:7</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:1\">1JN 3:1</a></p>\n<h3>Redemption through the death of Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom3:24\">ROM 3:24</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:7\">EPH 1:7</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim1:14-1Tim1:16\">1TI 1:14–1:16</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus2:13-Titus2:14\">TIT 2:13–2:14</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:18-1Pet1:19\">1PE 1:18–1:19</a></p>\n<h3>His gift of eternal life</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:16\">JHN 3:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:28\">JHN 10:28</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom3:23-Rom3:24\">ROM 3:23–3:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:17\">ROM 5:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom6:23\">ROM 6:23</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim1:14-1Tim1:16\">1TI 1:14–1:16</a></p>\n<h2>God's generosity experienced in sanctification</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:2-2Pet1:3\">2PE 1:2–1:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps23:5\">PSA 23:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps36:7-Ps36:8\">PSA 36:7–36:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek47:1-Ezek47:12\">EZK 47:1–47:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:12-Phil2:13\">PHP 2:12–2:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:19\">PHP 4:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:2\">JUD 1:2</a></p>\n<h3>The gift of the Holy Spirit</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel2:28-Joel2:29\">JOL 2:28–2:29</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:17-Acts2:18\">ACT 2:17–2:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek39:29\">EZK 39:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:34\">JHN 3:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:45\">ACT 10:45</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:5\">ROM 5:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus3:6\">TIT 3:6</a></p>\n<h3>Wisdom</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:5\">JAS 1:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:2\">COL 2:2</a></p>\n<h3>Comfort, strength and encouragement</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor1:5\">2CO 1:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph3:16\">EPH 3:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess2:16-2Thess2:17\">2TH 2:16–2:17</a></p>\n<h2>God's generosity in heaven</h2>\n<h3>Inheritance</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor2:9\">1CO 2:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:18\">EPH 1:18</a></p>\n<h3>Reward</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov28:20\">PRO 28:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:35\">HEB 10:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:1-Rev21:4\">REV 21:1–21:4</a></p>",
